{
  "texts": [
    "However, coverage is only a proxy measure for the bug-finding ability of a fuzzer [26], [10].",
    "Hence, we complement the coverage results with bug-finding results.Coverage.",
    "We report the coverage of both, the code and the state space.",
    "To evaluate code coverage, we measure the branch coverage achieved using the automated tooling provided by the benchmarking platform PROFUZZBENCH [33].",
    "To evaluate the coverage of the state space, we measure (i) the number of distinct states (state coverage) and the number of transitions between these states (transition coverage) using automatic tooling provided by the benchmarking platform."
  ]
}